OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and predominantly sunny to
OL,6,Fend the week. Feeling hot, with
OL,7,Fdaytime temperatures widely above the
OL,8,Faverage. Cooler closer to coasts with
OL,9,Fan onshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClear skies to start with
OL,12,Fsome thin high level cloud moving
OL,13,Fsouthwards overnight. Winds will be
OL,14,Flight and variable. Overnight
OL,15,Ftemperatures are expected to remain
OL,16,Frelatively warm overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
