OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry and largely sunny on
OL,6,FSaturday. A very warm day though
OL,7,Fcooler with coastal low cloud
OL,8,Flingering, this could push inland
OL,9,Fduring the evening as a northeasterly
OL,10,Fbreeze develops.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FLow
OL,13,Fcloud and patchy drizzle possible
OL,14,Fearly Sunday before brightening up.
OL,15,FDry and sunny by Monday. Tuesday will
OL,16,Fbe cloudy with patchy light rain
OL,17,Fpossible over higher ground.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
